OL,3,CMan charged after boiling water attack
OL,4,Cat Strabane courthouse
OL,6,FA 34-year-old man has been charged
OL,7,Fafter another man was doused with
OL,8,Fboiling water ahead of a murder case
OL,9,Fhearing.
OL,11,FThe victim was left with serious burn
OL,12,Fwounds after the incident at Strabane
OL,13,FMagistrates' Court on Thursday morning.
OL,15,FTrouble broke out in the court forcing
OL,16,Fthe district judge to halt proceedings.
OL,18,FIt was alleged the attacker used a
OL,19,Fkettle in the building before throwing
OL,20,Fwater over a man.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/4
