OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1776618353
OL,3,CMan charged after boiling water attack
OL,4,Cat Strabane courthouse
OL,6,FA man is charged with attempted
OL,7,Fgrievous bodily harm with intent,
OL,8,Fassault occasioning actual bodily harm
OL,9,Fand possession of an offensive weapon
OL,10,Fwith intent to commit an indictable
OL,11,Foffence.
OL,13,FHe is due to appear at Dungannon
OL,14,FMagistrates' Court on Saturday.
OL,16,FThe victim was the brother of Dylan
OL,17,FMcCrossan, 32, from Beechmount
OL,18,FVillage, Strabane, who is accused of
OL,19,Fthe murder of Stephen Holmes.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/4
