OL,3,CMan charged after boiling water attack
OL,4,Cat Strabane courthouse
OL,6,FMr Holmes, aged 31, died after an
OL,7,Fassault in Strabane in February 2025.
OL,9,FThe McCrossans are brothers to Daniel
OL,10,FMcCrossan, the SDLP West Tyrone MLA.
